data.description: Beautiful home in the Tierra Del Este Subdivision is ready for you! Close to Stone Rock Park. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers comfortable living with zero worries for lawn maintenance. Enjoy the spacious kitchen as well. The backyard features a large covered pergola and outdoor kitchen area (new grill installed) to include a working sink. Curb appeal, great area, close to shopping, dining, entertainment, parks and more. Don't miss your opportunity to own this amazing home.
